#   .--Desktops Registered-------------------------------------------------.
#   |               ____            _    _                                 |
#   |              |  _ \  ___  ___| | _| |_ ___  _ __  ___                |
#   |              | | | |/ _ \/ __| |/ / __/ _ \| '_ \/ __|               |
